extendedInfo.description: Looking for an ATM in Chiang Mai? Search no more! This application has all the information you need: * You can use it if you are in a car, on a bicycle or walking * You can view all ATMs on the map * You can search ATMs * You can view ATMs near you * You can view directions (visual route, distance and duration) * You can use it with Street View * You can use it with NavigationSupported banks: * AEON * Bank for Agriculture and Agricultural Cooperatives * Bank of Ayudhya * Bangkok Bank * CIMB Thai Bank * Government Housing Bank * Government Savings Bank * Kasikorn Bank * Krung Thai Bank * Siam Commercial Bank * Standard Chartered Bank * Thanachart Bank * TMB Bank * UOB Bank * and more!Keywords: chiang mai, thailand, atms, bank, street view, navigation, aeon, bank for agriculture and agricultural cooperatives, ayudhya, cimb thai, citibank, government housing, government savings, islamic, krung thai, kasikorn, siam commercial, siam city, standard chartered, thai credit, thanachart, tisco, tmb, uob
